Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真是看不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,決戰！亂馬能復活嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,敬請期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:37.39,ED,,0,0,0,,收下吧，MY SONG
